==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Loggat
<hw>Log"gat</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Also written
<ets>logget</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A small log or piece of
wood.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <pluf>pl.</pluf> <def>An old game in England, played by
throwing pieces of wood at a stake set in the ground.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Logge</ent>⟦br⟧
